ource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.9999999999481588, \"rank\": 4.124132980052807e-11, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grab a seat at the bar this summer and enjoy theCure Farm green saladfollowed by aNew York stripwith plum demi-glace, leek puree, radicchio, and grilled plums.\", \"from\": 5170, \"to\": 5329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Where:3200 Larimer St., Denver  When:Sunday 2 p.m. - 10 p.m., Monday 4 p.m. - 9 p.m., Tuesday - Thursday 4 p.m. - 10 p.m., Friday - Saturday 2 p.m. - 10 p.m.\", \"from\": 5331, \"to\": 5488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5342, \"end\": 5349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larimer_County,_Colorado\", \"score\": 0.9446013509524818, \"rank\": 0.05644192828958727, \"text\": \"Larimer\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larimer_County,_Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larimer_County,_Colorado\"}, {\"begin\": 5355, \"end\": 5361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.53779898117267e-19, \"text\": \"Denver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Lowdown:For those planning to plant themselves on the couch and catch all the events from gymnastics to swimming - pick up some cans of wine fromInfinite Monkey Theoremand toast the athletes with wine that is mountain grown and city made.\", \"from\": 5490, \"to\": 5732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, that is it.\", \"from\": 5734, \"to\": 5751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We hope you enjoyed this guided tour of dining experiences and that you also enjoy watching the 2024 Paris Summer Games.\", \"from\": 5752, \"to\": 5872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you liked this guide and would like to see 